---
const imageUrl = '/images/edition-002-cover-background-purple.webp'
const balloonUrl = '/images/hot-air-balloon.webp'
const buttonUrl = '/editions/third-edition'
---

<section class="py-62">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
      <div class="relative inline-block">
        <img src={imageUrl} alt="Nomad Magazine Edition 002 covers" class="w-full max-w-xl" loading="lazy" />
        <img src={balloonUrl} alt="Hot air balloon" class="absolute -top-28 -right-2 h-auto w-64" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="mb-8 text-6xl font-bold">Welcome to the family, Nomad!</h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-lg text-neutral-400">
      Nomad Magazine aspires to unravel the <a href="/blog/wander-in-style-the-ultimate-guide-to-travel-fashion-trends" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200">hacks, secrets and whereabouts</a> of this daring tribe that has transformed the very essence of modern <a href="/blog/7-tips-for-balancing-work-and-travel" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200">work and travel</a>.
    </p>
    <div class="mb-8">
      <p class="text-base text-neutral-400">
        Ready to join the nomadic lifestyle? Check out our <a href="/blog/best-digital-nomad-jobs-for-beginners-in-2025-start-your-remote-career-today" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200">beginner's guide</a> to remote work or explore <a href="/blog/what-are-the-trending-digital-nomad-cities" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200">trending nomad cities</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a href={buttonUrl} class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-yellow-400 px-8 py-3 font-bold text-black"> Buy Now </a>
  </div>
</section>
